sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant AuthProxy as Auth Proxy<br/>(kube-rbac-proxy/oauth-proxy)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant REST as OVMS REST Handler<br/>rest_port/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as OVMS gRPC Handler<br/>grpc_port/TCP gRPC
    participant KFS as KServe v2 Service
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI Chat Handler<br/>(MediaPipe)
    participant CB as Continuous Batching<br/>Pipeline
    participant MM as Model Manager
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant HFPull as HF Pull Module
    participant S3 as S3/Azure/GCS<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,OV: Flow 1: KServe v2 Inference Request

    Client->>AuthProxy: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    AuthProxy->>REST: Forward (plaintext HTTP)<br/>rest_port/TCP
    REST->>KFS: Route to KFS inference service<br/>(internal function call)
    KFS->>MM: Resolve model instance<br/>(version, status check)
    MM->>OV: Execute inference<br/>(in-process)
    OV-->>MM: Inference result tensor
    MM-->>KFS: Prediction output
    KFS-->>REST: KServe v2 response
    REST-->>AuthProxy: HTTP response
    AuthProxy-->>Client: HTTPS response (JSON)

    Note over Client,OV: Flow 2: LLM Chat Completion (Streaming SSE)

    Client->>AuthProxy: POST /v3/{name}/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/8443, stream=true
    AuthProxy->>REST: Forward (plaintext HTTP)<br/>rest_port/TCP
    REST->>OpenAI: Route to OpenAI Chat Handler<br/>(MediaPipe graph)
    OpenAI->>CB: Submit to Continuous Batching Pipeline<br/>(dynamic batching, max_num_seqs=256)
    loop Token Generation
        CB->>OV: Generate next token<br/>(OpenVINO GenAI)
        OV-->>CB: Token output
        CB-->>OpenAI: Stream token
        OpenAI-->>REST: SSE chunk
        REST-->>AuthProxy: HTTP chunked/SSE
        AuthProxy-->>Client: SSE data: {"choices":[...]}
    end
    OpenAI-->>REST: SSE [DONE]
    REST-->>AuthProxy: Final SSE chunk
    AuthProxy-->>Client: data: [DONE]

    Note over HFPull,HF: Flow 3: Model Pull from HuggingFace

    Note right of HFPull: Triggered by CLI --pull flag
    HFPull->>HF: Git clone (libgit2)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: HF Token (optional)
    HF-->>HFPull: Repository contents
    Note right of HFPull: OR for GGUF models:
    HFPull->>HF: HTTPS download (curl)<br/>443/TCP, CURLSSLOPT_NATIVE_CA<br/>Auth: HF Token (optional)
    HF-->>HFPull: GGUF model file
    HFPull->>MM: Register downloaded model<br/>(local filesystem)

    Note over MM,S3: Flow 4: Model Loading from Cloud Storage

    MM->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / Azure / GCP credentials
    S3-->>MM: Model files (binary)
    MM->>OV: Load model into OpenVINO Runtime
    OV-->>MM: Model ready for inference
